seo: Duomicms,SQL注入漏洞,漏洞检测,安全测试
summary: 该插件用于检测Duomicms系统中的SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定的HTTP请求并分析响应来确认是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in the Duomicms system by sending specific HTTP requests and analyzing the responses to confirm whether there are any vulnerabilities.
